snippet.title: Chalvo 55 - Nintendo Gameboy (Gameplay Video)
snippet.description:
Chalvo 55 is a Puzzle / Platformer developed by Japan System Supply in 1997. It was only released in Japan and is not seen too often, most likely due to the Gameboy Color being released months later.

The game is the successor of the unreleased Virtual Boy game, Bound High.
